metadata.name: Vita Aeterna I
metadata.description:
VITA AETERNAE is a 1/1 series exploring the blurred lines between life, death and eternity. Each piece exists on its own and as a part of the whole and was created in collab with AI. The collection is limited to six pieces, starting at 0.66 ETH each. 
The collector who owns all six pieces of Vita Aeterna will receive a physical Bronze Bas-Relief in the size of 20x20 cm
